{"tid":1627342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"金管局: 逾330櫃員機受損 約150部沒足夠現金","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:35:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e381d340d73ed5b1a4bf8d1d820e58619ecacaf","tid":1627342,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"金管局今晚提供最新數字，發言人稱，全港總數約3300部銀行櫃員機中，約超過10%、即逾330部受損而不能正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n在運作正常櫃員機之中，有約5%的櫃員機，因各種原因有待補充現金而未能提供提款服務。即約150部櫃員機沒有足夠現金。<br />\n<br />\n有關上述兩項數字，當局均未有指明涉及哪些銀行的櫃員機。<br />\n<br />\n金管局發言人又指，由於港鐵車站及部分商場關閉，車站或商場內的櫃員機今日未能提供服務。銀行正與現鈔運送服務商加緊協調，在可行的情況下盡快補充現金，令櫃員機恢復運作。銀行業界希望櫃盡快恢復受影響的服務，令對市民影響減至最低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1570288593403&amp;issue=20191005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1570288593403%26issue%3D20191005&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=22c5ac47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1570288593403&amp;issue=20191005</a>"},{"pid":"ffc19b349943396db07bee4aaae690069c9b2fe8","tid":1627342,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1f02fa3bf45ceee32dcab579594928e51d2dea","tid":1627342,"uid":295981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"一係唔㩒錢，一㩒就㩒盡佢！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1626821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1626821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推呀"},{"pid":"b9fa655456f7ca764e080ba28533060c104c84b1","tid":1627342,"uid":98681,"like":0,"disli